title: German Streamer
body:
Heyho! We just started streaming and we would be cheered if u support us ! We r currently trying to climb from Plat elo into Diamond V. We enjoy playing League and are passionate about it. We are funny guys and try to make a leaving out of that. 
Vielen Dank! 

Stream: www.twitch.tv/ahlizko
Ign: Selizko, Ahdryn

Wir sind 18, 19 Jahre alt und sind ziemlich funny. Wir würden uns über follows und Unterstützung freuen. Seid bei unserem Climb dabei :>
